      <div class="achievement-card"><div class="achievement-emoji">🎉</div><div class="achievement-title">Sarah 通過英檢初級</div><div class="achievement-desc">口說與寫作皆高分</div></div>
      <div class="achievement-card"><div class="achievement-emoji">🎓</div><div class="achievement-title">Bella 碩士榜首</div><div class="achievement-desc">錄取體育大學推廣系</div></div>
