      <div class="achievement-card"><div class="achievement-emoji">🎓</div><div class="achievement-title">Queenie 錄取台大碩士</div><div class="achievement-desc">園藝暨景觀學系</div></div>
      <div class="achievement-card"><div class="achievement-emoji">🎉</div><div class="achievement-title">Cherry 作文 16.5 分</div><div class="achievement-desc">114 學測作文高分</div></div>
      <div class="achievement-card"><div class="achievement-emoji">🎉</div><div class="achievement-title">Oliver 小四過英檢</div><div class="achievement-desc">取得初級證書</div></div>
      <div class="achievement-card"><div class="achievement-emoji">🎓</div><div class="achievement-title">Ian 錄取彰師大碩士</div><div class="achievement-desc">統計資訊研究所</div></div>
